SUMMARY:Wednesday Late Mornings Brunch Rides  Casual Pace Variable Distanc
 e
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Bicycle Club (LBC) Meetup\nAs the mornings grow cold
 er it is time to ride later in the mornings\nEvery Wednesday late morning.
 ..Ride and eat Yummy brunch together.\nPlease do not go on this ride unles
 s you will ride at a casual pace and stay with the group . We will meet to
  ride to brunch at a casual pace. After eating some may split up with some
  returning to the start and others going longer and faster.\nHelmets are m
 andatory\; No ear buds or audible music playing devices. Please bring wate
 r\, and a basic repair kit (spare tube\, tire levers\, pump/CO2 inflator).
 \nTo eliminate passing around a pen and paper waiver\, we encourage LBC Cl
 ub membership and Meetup RSVP below to join this ride. RSVP also allows us
  to contact you after the ride if needed. If you do not RSVP you are not c
 overed by the club excess accident insurance policy\; only club members wh
 o RSVP are covered. Being on Meetup does not mean you are a club member. J
 oin here- https://www.lancasterbikeclub.net/content.aspx?page_id=60&club_i
 d=257148\nRichard Conner\, leader717-572-8480
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/lancaster-bicycle-club/events/3136512
 14/
