SUMMARY:IMPROPMTU- BI Bird In Hand Bakeshop (23F) -- RSVP required
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Bicycle Club (LBC) Meetup\nRide Leader: Bruce Black\
 n\nA mostly flat ride through eastern Lancaster County. The pace will be b
 etween 14 and 16mph with multiple stop and regroup points.\n\n• “short
 ” stop for refreshment/coffee mid-route at Bird In Hand Bakeshop\nThis r
 ide is a social ride\, but cyclists are not expected to stay in one group.
  Cyclists may pedal at their own comfortable paces. Please be supportive o
 f the other cyclists to avoid anyone biking alone or being dropped off the
  back of the last group.\n\nClick for [Ride with GPS](https://ridewithgps.
 com/routes/54352043)\n\nHelmets are mandatory. No ear buds. Please bring w
 ater and a basic repair kit (spare tube\, tire levers\, pump/CO2 inflator)
 .\n\nTo eliminate passing around a pen and paper waiver\, we require LBC C
 lub membership and Meetup RSVP below to join this ride.\n\nBeing on Meetup
  does not mean you are a club member. [Join here](https://www.lancasterbik
 eclub.net/content.aspx?page_id=60&club_id=257148).\n\nYour RSVP is your ag
 reement to abide by the club's [Code of Conduct](https://lancbikeclub.club
 express.com/content.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=257148&module_id=323984) \,\n[
 Rules of the Road](https://lancbikeclub.clubexpress.com/content.aspx?page_
 id=22&club_id=257148&module_id=325159) \, and [Ride Waiver](https://lancas
 terbikeclub.net/docs.ashx?id=454318)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/lancaster-bicycle-club/events/3139125
 37/
